  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/10/russian-authorities-reject-bitcoin/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/3099df6e52c6e99dc15ad40974d23df1/putin-lead2.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n交给索契冬奥会官方的筹办经费，近年来在国际上争议不断的<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/bitcoin\">比特币</a>，这两者之间哪个风险更大？别人不知道，俄罗斯政府的答案显然是后者。他们的中央银行日前在一份声明重表示，这种虚拟货币极容易贬值，而且可能会诱使持有者支持非法活动或是「资助恐怖主义」。<br />\n<br />\n和之前发布「<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/05/china-warns-banks-against-dealing-in-bitcoin-btc/\">比特币风险通知</a>」的我国相比，俄罗斯面对这种「货币替代品」的态度更加<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/04/congressional-bitcoin-report/\">坚决</a>，直接做到了全面禁止的地步。按照总检察署的说法，卢布仍是俄罗斯的唯一官方货币，比特币什么的，免谈啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/10/russian-authorities-reject-bitcoin/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.slashgear.com/bitcoin-deem-illegal-by-russian-authorities-10316262/\" target=\"_blank\">SlashGear</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/09/us-russia-bitcoin-idUSBREA1806620140209\" target=\"_blank\">Reuters</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/10/russian-authorities-reject-bitcoin/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20826813/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/10/russian-authorities-reject-bitcoin/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
